  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "### Recreate With Loops\r\n\r\nEvie went back to a track she made before she learned about loops. She wants to recreate it using loops instead:\r\n\r\n> I found a lot of little combinations that I liked and repeated them in different patterns. But the code got so long - now with loops, I can just repeat each chunk as many times as I want.\r\n\r\nLook for **patterns** in Evie's code and identify the parts that can be converted into loops.\r\n\r\nAll of the blocks you need are already in the workspace. You can replace her old code with your new code as soon as you drag-and-drop on top of it!",
    "offer_browser_tts": "true",
    "use_secondary_finish_button": "false",
    "hide_share_and_remix": "true",
